		<p>Karl is a French actor and filmmaker.</p>
		<p>He is a household name in French TV, and the face of various world wide campaigns. His leading roles in episodic TV shows -  Metal Hurlant Chronicles, Profilage, S.D.R  amongst many others - repeatedly establish new primetime viewer records, with his episodes garnering awards. In "Les Fauves" we see Karl - playing the lead role - take down a mafia unit as an undercover cop.</p>
		<p>Karl was also part of  the exclusive stunt team hand selected by Luc Besson, which brought « District 13 », « Transporter 3 », and many more to our screens. His first two features were helmed by Jean Marc Barr (The Big Blue).  Today he spends most of his time in the US, diving into the world of indie filmmaking. He co-stared in « Layover » which has run in many US film festivals.</p>
		<p>He’s also very active behind the camera. His directorial debut  « DuO » is a colorful short movie made in 48 hours.  He is  currently developing several indie projects.</p>
